text: Jordyn Woods (born 23 September 1997, Los Angeles, California) is an American model, entrepreneur, socialite, singer, and YouTuber. She is known for her role on the reality television show Life of Kylie and for her YouTube videos. == Modeling career == In 2015, an agent found Jordyn Woods on Instagram and asked if she wanted to be a model. In May 2016, she walked her first runway in a fashion show. Woods also worked as a model for Good American, a Khlo√© Kardashian clothing brand. In 2017, she walked in New York Fashion Week for the first time. In 2019, she was on the cover of the magazine Cosmopolitan UK. == References == Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Models from Los Angeles Category:Singers from Los Angeles Category:Businesspeople from Los Angeles
